I"<h1 class="no_toc" id="adjusting-symbology">Adjusting Symbology</h1>
<p>Now we are going to change the symbology of the Deaths and Broad St. Pump so that they are more visible.  Follow the steps as outlined and refer to the video below.</p>

<hr />

<details open="">
  <summary class="text-delta">
